businesses.name: Plant Strong Coaching
businesses.business_details:
I began Plant Strong Coaching in 2015 when I saw a need within the local community for personalised health and fitness coaching. My experience in health and fitness stems from being involved in sport at an elite level.

I offer a wide range of services, from all forms of cardio (HIIT, circuit, MetCcon) to strength and hypertrophy
training.
businesses.product_details:
Plant Strong Coaching offers face-to-face and online personal training services, from private to group fitness
coaching. These workouts are uniquely designed to suit your needs.
businesses.new_products:
- Plant Strong Coaching now offers online personal workouts, so everything can be done from the comfort of your home, no matter whether you have fitness equipment or not. All workouts have exercise demonstration videos to assist you. 
- Outdoor sessions in Abbotsford area (within current social distancing regulations of course)
